---
title: Tomato and Prawn Risotto with rocket side salad
description: Too complex to cook? Not with our easy to follow recipe! You won't believe how simple it is to whip yourself up a plate of perfectly al dente prawn risotto with bursting balsamic tomatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF190424_R04_W22_NL_R1475_Main_high-b710ba53.jpg
